Addresses #33

Doorhangers will not appear when Tracking Protection & "Do Not Track" preferences are set to "Always".  Both preferences must be set, even when using a Private Window, for doorhanger to be disabled.

fixes input scrolling / presentation issue when characters with descenders are entered.
